imlib2: imlib2 (Imlib 2 Graphics Library)
imlib2:
imlib2: Imlib 2 is the successor to Imlib. It is a completely new library. 
imlib2: Imlib 2 can be installed alongside Imlib 1.x without any problems 
imlib2: since they are effectively different libraries which have very 
imlib2: similar functionality. 
imlib2:
imlib2: Imlib 2 was written by Carsten Haitzler.
imlib2:
